'''Glyptology''' is the study of engraved gems, or of engravings on gems.<ref>{{cite news|title=Four seniors, one alumnus receive Gates Cambridge Scholarships|url=https://www.princeton.edu/pr/pwb/03/0602/5b.shtml|accessdate=February 20, 2018|work=Princeton Weekly Bulletin|publisher=[[Princeton University]]|date=June 2, 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Eccentric Maxwell Sommerville|url=https://www.penn.museum/sites/expedition/the-eccentric-maxwell-sommerville/|website=[[University of Pennsylvania Museum of Archaeology and Anthropology]]|publisher=[[University of Pennsylvania]]|accessdate=February 20, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Thorpe|first1=Edgar|title=The Pearson General Knowledge Manual 2012|date=2012|publisher=Pearson Education|isbn=8131761908|page=B5}}</ref>
